      </details>

      <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1rem;">
        <summary style="font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;">Can I see a telehealth psychologist in Sydney for health anxiety via Medicare?</summary>
